### Register initiate
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register/initiate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass1"
}

### Register verify
### temp_token (checks access token from cookie)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "otp": "123456",
}

### Resend OTP
### temp_token (checks access token from cookie)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register/resend-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass1"
}

### Refresh token (from Authorization header)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/token/refresh
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN

### Validate token (checks access token from cookie, refreshes if expired using refresh cookie)
### Tokens are read from httpOnly cookies, not from Authorization header
### Requires cookies: access_token (optional for refresh), refresh_token (optional as fallback)
GET http://localhost:8000/auth/token/validate

### Forgot password
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/password/forgot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com"
}

### Validate reset token
GET http://localhost:8000/auth/password/reset/validate?token=RESET_TOKEN_FROM_EMAIL

### Reset password
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/password/reset?token=RESET_TOKEN_FROM_EMAIL
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "new_password": "StrongerPass2"
}
